## Limitations

The analysis is limited by the availability of sources and the potential bias in historical interpretations. Many sources reflect a predominantly American perspective, which may not fully capture the global implications of Reconstruction. Additionally, the complexity of the era means that some nuances and regional variations in the Reconstruction experience may not be fully addressed in this report.